  <brief_title>Acticoat Absorbent and BCT Antimicrobial for STSG Donor Site on Thigh</brief_title>
  <official_title>Acticoat Absorbent and BCT Antimicrobial for STSG Donor Site on Thigh---A Randomised Controlled Trial</official_title>
